# RNA-seq Analysis Pipeline (Bash-Orchestrated HPC Version)

A comprehensive, modular RNA-seq analysis pipeline designed for High-Performance Computing (HPC) environments. This pipeline automates the entire RNA-seq workflow from raw FASTQ files to differential expression analysis and visualization, ensuring reproducibility and scalability for large transcriptomic datasets.

